Package com.coronis.exception

Exception Summary
BadlyFormattedFrameException This type of exception is thrown by the state machine parsing the Coronis frames on the InputStream.
CommandException Exception thrown when a 0x00 has been received from the WavePort.
ConfigException Exception thrown when their is something not configured correctly (missing paramater, bad value, etc.)
CoronisException Base Coronis exception for the JWaveLib.
MissingDataException Exception thrown when some missing data are found where it should not appear !
NoAckException Exception thrown when a NACK frame is received.
TimeOutException Exception thrown when a timeout has been encountered during a WavePort communication
TransmissionException Thrown when a transmission exception has been received (0x31)
UnsupportedFrameException Thrown by te CoronisFrameBuilder when the CMD is not supported
